## 8. Custom Scalars (RECOMMENDED)

**Use custom scalars for domain-specific types:**

```graphql
# scalars.graphqls
scalar DateTime  # ISO-8601 timestamp
scalar Date      # ISO-8601 date (no time)
scalar Email     # Validated email address
scalar URL       # Validated URL
scalar JSON      # Arbitrary JSON object
```

**Implementation (Spring GraphQL):**
```java
@Configuration
public class ScalarConfiguration {
    @Bean
    public RuntimeWiringConfigurer runtimeWiringConfigurer() {
        return wiringBuilder -> wiringBuilder
            .scalar(ExtendedScalars.DateTime)
            .scalar(ExtendedScalars.Date)
            .scalar(ExtendedScalars.Url)
            .scalar(ExtendedScalars.Json);
    }
}
```

